        "text": "Approximately five minutes later the object appeared again having reappeared\nfrom approximately the same location from which it had disappeared. The object\nwas seen again five minutes later for approximately ten second."
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "약 5분 후, 물체는 사라졌던 거의 같은 위치에서 다시 나타났다.\n물체는 약 10초 동안 5분 후에 다시 목격되었다.",
